headline: Blackstone to Present at the Goldman Sachs 2025 US Financial Services Conference
summary: NEW YORK, November 20, 2025--Blackstone (NYSE:BX) announced today that Jon Gray, President and Chief Operating Officer, is scheduled to present at the Goldman Sachs 2025 US Financial Services Conference on Wednesday, December 10, 2025 at 12:20pm ET.
